                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_60304156014730221.png",
